snippet.title: homebound | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Tasked on a mission to discover a new home planet, a lonely astronaut braves an desolate world while making a fluffy new friend.

homebound is a 2D puzzle platformer that follows an astronaut and a cat as they investigate an abandoned planet.
